	<longdescription>
		Libtorrent-rasterbar is a fork of libtorrent, a C++ bittorrent
		implementation. It's main goals are to be efficient and easy to use.

		It supports many extensions as microTP, DHT extensions, UDP
		trackers, HTTP seeding and more. Besides that it has bindings
		for Go, Java, Python and Node.
